title: Diamond ADC LF Support Duo for new Ranked Season
body:
Hi, as the title suggests, I'm looking for people to duo ranked with in new season. 

Highly prefer support players to play bot lane with, but if you play other roles and wanna duo I'm cool with that as well. 

If interested, then reply to this thread and/or add me in League. My IGN is Plutó.

Cheers.
